!!!! Commit [[1d97d53|https://github.com/CrossEye/TW5-SimpleOutlinePlugin/commit/1d97d53381a6a5d8cedf730c655b71e6589871b8]] (2026-04-13)

```
group-by on ++ filter lines

group-by:field — buckets filter results by a tiddler field into collapsible
group nodes (one per distinct value; tiddlers with no value fall into a
'(none)' group).

group-by:<<procedure>> — invokes a procedure once per tiddler with
currentTiddler set; the plain-text output is used as the group key, enabling
arbitrary computed grouping (e.g. decade bucketing via a \function + \procedure
pair using filter arithmetic: divide/floor/multiply).

Add Grouped Filter Demo with field and procedure examples.
Add year and period fields to the 17 History of Computing note tiddlers.
Backfill changelog entries for 0.9.1 and 0.10.0.
```

!!!! Commit (2026-04-13)

```
group-by on ++ filter lines
```

`++` filter lines now accept an optional `group-by:value` option.  Supply a field name to bucket results by that field (`group-by:period`), or a procedure call to compute a key per tiddler (`group-by:<<decade>>`).  Tiddlers with no value for the field fall into a `(none)` group.  Groups render as collapsible nodes with the matching items as children.  Add Grouped Filter Demo with field and procedure examples.

